career_guidance_backend/
│
├── app.py                  # Main application entry point
├── config.py               # Configuration (Database URI, Secret Key, etc.)
├── requirements.txt        # List of dependencies
├── database.db             # SQLite database (auto-generated)
├── models.py               # Database models (Students, Colleges, etc.)
│
├── routes/                  # API route logic
│   ├── __init__.py         # Makes it a Python package
│   ├── auth.py             # Signup & Login related endpoints
│   ├── profile.py          # Profile management endpoints
│   ├── recommendation.py   # Career recommendation logic
│   ├── colleges.py         # Colleges info endpoints
│   ├── scholarships.py     # Scholarship info endpoints
│   └── notifications.py    # Notifications logic
│
├── services/                # (Optional) Business logic layer
│   └── career_service.py   # Recommendation engine logic, etc.
│
├── utils/                   # (Optional) Helper functions
│   └── helpers.py          # e.g., for sending emails or processing input
│
├── static/                  # Static files (optional)
│   └── images/             # Example folder for images
│
├── templates/                # HTML templates (optional if not using frontend)
│   └── index.html
│
└── README.md                # Project overview and instructions


“EduGuidely”, “LearnBridge”, or “GrowWise”